latestIgtvVideos.title: Healthy & Happy Skincare Routine!🧖
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
||Exfoliate, Moisturize, Rejuvenate and that glow though||😍
.
STEP 1. Cleansing, includes facewash @good_vibes.in & Scrub.
STEP 2. Toning, includes rose water & aloevera gel.
STEP 3. Facepack, includes multani mitti, rose water & lime juice.
STEP 4. Hydration, includes vitamin e capsule & moisturizer.
.
||SCRUB||🌹
2 tablespoons COFFEE
2 tablespoons SUGAR
1 tablespoon ALOVERA GEL
1 tablespoon HONEY
.
Benefits-:✨
•Tightens & Brightens skin
•Removes dead skin cells
•Removes tanning
•Reduces Puffiness
•Fastens Blood Circulation
.
||FACEPACK||🌹
2 tablespoons FULLER'S EARTH (multani mitti)
1 tablespoon ROSE WATER
1 tablespoon LIME JUICE
.
 (my every weekend reliever.)
I have a combination skin type and this facepack suits super good on my skin. I use it once every week. It absorbs excess oil from the skin and is very helpful in preventing pimples and acne!
 .
 Safeguard ⬇️
•Always wet your skin before exfoliation.
•Make sure to check it on a small area of your skin before applying on full. 
•Do not over exfoliate or it can cause you itching or irritation.
•Moisturize well after scrubbing.
.
(vs:the last part was not in my routine it's just for the video :,-) love yourself. (MY NO MAKE-UP, MAKE-UP LOOK!)🍹
.
•Now, Happy You!❤️
